.SYNOPSIS
    This PowerShell script ensures that the Windows Installer policy "AlwaysInstallElevated" is disabled (set to 0),
    preventing standard users from installing MSI packages with elevated privileges.

.NOTES
    Author          : Salman Nur
    LinkedIn        : linkedin.com/in/salman-nur-112aa225b/
    GitHub          : github.com/salmananur
    Date Created    : 2026-04-01
